{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1015,"text":"You may never have heard\nof Kenema, Sierra Leone"},{"time":3801,"text":"or Arua, Nigeria."},{"time":5357,"text":"But I know them as two of the most\nextraordinary places on earth."}]},{"cues":[{"time":9956,"text":"In hospitals there, there's a community\nof nurses, physicians and scientists"},{"time":15033,"text":"that have been quietly battling"},{"time":16614,"text":"one of the deadliest threats\nto humanity for years:"},{"time":19338,"text":"Lassa virus."},{"time":21118,"text":"Lassa virus is a lot like Ebola."},{"time":23280,"text":"It can cause a severe fever\nand can often be fatal."},{"time":27053,"text":"But these individuals,\nthey risk their lives every day"},{"time":31016,"text":"to protect the individuals\nin their communities,"},{"time":33957,"text":"and by doing so, protect us all."}]},{"cues":[{"time":37093,"text":"But one of the most extraordinary things\nI learned about them"},{"time":40025,"text":"on one of my first visits\nout there many years ago"},{"time":42616,"text":"was that they start each morning --"},{"time":44349,"text":"these challenging, extraordinary days\non the front lines -- by singing."},{"time":49731,"text":"They gather together,\nand they show their joy."},{"time":53094,"text":"They show their spirit."},{"time":54640,"text":"And over the years,"},{"time":55823,"text":"from year after year as I've visited them\nand they've visited me,"},{"time":58960,"text":"I get to gather with them and I sing"},{"time":60977,"text":"and we write and we love it,"},{"time":63175,"text":"because it reminds us that we're not\njust there to pursue science together;"},{"time":66742,"text":"we're bonded through a shared humanity."}]},{"cues":[{"time":69586,"text":"And that of course, as you can imagine,\nbecomes extremely important,"},{"time":73933,"text":"even essential, as things begin to change."},{"time":76730,"text":"And that changed a great deal\nin March of 2014,"},{"time":81543,"text":"when the Ebola outbreak\nwas declared in Guinea."},{"time":84426,"text":"This is the first outbreak in West Africa,"},{"time":86582,"text":"near the border\nof Sierra Leone and Liberia."},{"time":90074,"text":"And it was frightening,\nfrightening for us all."},{"time":92620,"text":"We had actually suspected for some time"},{"time":94556,"text":"that Lassa and Ebola were more\nwidespread than thought,"},{"time":97222,"text":"and we thought it could\none day come to Kenema."}]},{"cues":[{"time":99896,"text":"And so members of my team\nimmediately went out"},{"time":102330,"text":"and joined Dr. Humarr Khan\nand his team there,"},{"time":104751,"text":"and we set up diagnostics to be able\nto have sensitive molecular tests"},{"time":108452,"text":"to pick up Ebola if it came\nacross the border"},{"time":110629,"text":"and into Sierra Leone."},{"time":111916,"text":"We'd already set up this kind\nof capacity for Lassa virus,"},{"time":114936,"text":"we knew how to do it,"},{"time":116117,"text":"the team is outstanding."},{"time":117571,"text":"We just had to give them\nthe tools and place to survey for Ebola."}]},{"cues":[{"time":121340,"text":"And unfortunately, that day came."},{"time":122992,"text":"On May 23, 2014, a woman checked\ninto the maternity ward at the hospital,"},{"time":127997,"text":"and the team ran\nthose important molecular tests"},{"time":131747,"text":"and they identified the first\nconfirmed case of Ebola in Sierra Leone."},{"time":136107,"text":"This was an exceptional\nwork that was done."},{"time":138180,"text":"They were able to diagnose\nthe case immediately,"},{"time":140464,"text":"to safely treat the patient"},{"time":142801,"text":"and to begin to do contact tracing\nto follow what was going on."},{"time":145843,"text":"It could've stopped something."},{"time":147839,"text":"But by the time that day came,"},{"time":150710,"text":"the outbreak had already\nbeen breeding for months."},{"time":153092,"text":"With hundreds of cases, it had already\neclipsed all previous outbreaks."},{"time":156756,"text":"And it came into Sierra Leone\nnot as that singular case,"},{"time":160424,"text":"but as a tidal wave."}]},{"cues":[{"time":162120,"text":"We had to work\nwith the international community,"},{"time":164419,"text":"with the Ministry of Health, with Kenema,\nto begin to deal with the cases,"},{"time":168149,"text":"as the next week brought 31,"},{"time":170244,"text":"then 92, then 147 cases --\nall coming to Kenema,"},{"time":173942,"text":"one of the only places in Sierra Leone\nthat could deal with this."}]},{"cues":[{"time":177610,"text":"And we worked around the clock\ntrying to do everything we could,"},{"time":181033,"text":"trying to help the individuals,\ntrying to get attention,"},{"time":184018,"text":"but we also did one other simple thing."},{"time":186544,"text":"From that specimen that we take\nfrom a patient's blood to detect Ebola,"},{"time":190357,"text":"we can discard it, obviously."},{"time":192436,"text":"The other thing we can do is, actually,\nput in a chemical and deactivate it,"},{"time":196076,"text":"so just place it into a box\nand ship it across the ocean,"},{"time":198830,"text":"and that's what we did."},{"time":200005,"text":"We sent it to Boston, where my team works."},{"time":202724,"text":"And we also worked around the clock\ndoing shift work, day after day,"},{"time":206585,"text":"and we quickly generated 99 genomes\nof the Ebola virus."},{"time":210478,"text":"This is the blueprint -- the genome\nof a virus is the blueprint."},{"time":213559,"text":"We all have one."},{"time":214742,"text":"It says everything that makes up us,"},{"time":216711,"text":"and it tells us so much information."}]},{"cues":[{"time":218644,"text":"The results of this kind of work\nare simple and they're powerful."},{"time":222396,"text":"We could actually take\nthese 99 different viruses,"},{"time":224890,"text":"look at them and compare them,"},{"time":226361,"text":"and we could see, actually,\ncompared to three genomes"},{"time":229231,"text":"that had been previously\npublished from Guinea,"},{"time":232091,"text":"we could show that the outbreak\nemerged in Guinea months before,"},{"time":235826,"text":"once into the human population,"},{"time":237692,"text":"and from there had been transmitting\nfrom human to human."},{"time":240388,"text":"Now, that's incredibly important"},{"time":241956,"text":"when you're trying to figure out\nhow to intervene,"},{"time":244348,"text":"but the important thing\nis contact tracing."},{"time":246438,"text":"We also could see that as the virus\nwas moving between humans,"},{"time":249864,"text":"it was mutating."},{"time":251145,"text":"And each of those mutations\nare so important,"},{"time":253320,"text":"because the diagnostics, the vaccines,"},{"time":255664,"text":"the therapies that we're using,"},{"time":257173,"text":"are all based on that genome\nsequence, fundamentally --"},{"time":260555,"text":"that's what drives it."},{"time":261800,"text":"And so global health experts\nwould need to respond,"},{"time":264706,"text":"would have to develop,"},{"time":265927,"text":"to recalibrate everything\nthat they were doing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":269079,"text":"But the way that science works,\nthe position I was in at that point"},{"time":272284,"text":"is, I had the data,"},{"time":273459,"text":"and I could have worked\nin a silo for many, many months,"},{"time":276119,"text":"analyzed the data carefully, slowly,"},{"time":278342,"text":"submitted the paper for publication,\ngone through a few back-and-forths,"},{"time":281826,"text":"and then finally when the paper came out,\nmight release that data."},{"time":284979,"text":"That's the way the status quo works."}]},{"cues":[{"time":287207,"text":"Well, that was not going to work\nat this point, right?"},{"time":289802,"text":"We had friends on the front lines"},{"time":291434,"text":"and to us it was just obvious\nthat what we needed is help,"},{"time":294712,"text":"lots of help."},{"time":295892,"text":"So the first thing we did is,"},{"time":297313,"text":"as soon as the sequences\ncame off the machines,"},{"time":300022,"text":"we published it to the web."},{"time":301475,"text":"We just released it to the whole world\nand said, \"Help us.\""},{"time":304335,"text":"And help came."}]},{"cues":[{"time":305694,"text":"Before we knew it,"},{"time":306880,"text":"we were being contacted\nfrom people all over,"},{"time":309240,"text":"surprised to see the data\nout there and released."},{"time":311708,"text":"Some of the greatest\nviral trackers in the world"},{"time":313984,"text":"were suddenly part of our community."},{"time":316087,"text":"We were working together\nin this virtual way,"},{"time":318441,"text":"sharing, regular calls, communications,"},{"time":321446,"text":"trying to follow the virus\nminute by minute,"},{"time":324221,"text":"to see ways that we could stop it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":327027,"text":"And there are so many ways\nthat we can form communities like that."},{"time":331182,"text":"Everybody, particularly when the outbreak\nstarted to expand globally,"},{"time":335531,"text":"was reaching out to learn,\nto participate, to engage."},{"time":339788,"text":"Everybody wants to play a part."},{"time":341406,"text":"The amount of human capacity\nout there is just amazing,"},{"time":344210,"text":"and the Internet connects us all."},{"time":345957,"text":"And could you imagine that instead\nof being frightened of each other,"},{"time":349232,"text":"that we all just said, \"Let's do this."},{"time":351113,"text":"Let's work together,\nand let's make this happen.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":353660,"text":"But the problem is that the data\nthat all of us are using,"},{"time":356426,"text":"Googling on the web, is just too limited\nto do what we need to do."},{"time":360487,"text":"And so many opportunities\nget missed when that happens."},{"time":363162,"text":"So in the early part\nof the epidemic from Kenema,"},{"time":365667,"text":"we'd had 106 clinical records\nfrom patients,"},{"time":368433,"text":"and we once again made that\npublicly available to the world."},{"time":371291,"text":"And in our own lab, we could show\nthat you could take those 106 records,"},{"time":374985,"text":"we could train computers to predict\nthe prognosis for Ebola patients"},{"time":378627,"text":"to near 100 percent accuracy."},{"time":380428,"text":"And we made an app\nthat could release that,"},{"time":382549,"text":"to make that available\nto health-care workers in the field."}]},{"cues":[{"time":385343,"text":"But 106 is just not enough\nto make it powerful,"},{"time":388626,"text":"to validate it."},{"time":389801,"text":"So we were waiting for more data\nto release that."},{"time":392479,"text":"and the data has still not come."},{"time":394547,"text":"We are still waiting, tweaking away,"},{"time":397103,"text":"in silos rather than working together."},{"time":399965,"text":"And this just -- we can't accept that."},{"time":402221,"text":"Right? You, all of you,\ncannot accept that."},{"time":406049,"text":"It's our lives on the line."},{"time":407755,"text":"And in fact, actually,"},{"time":409490,"text":"many lives were lost,\nmany health-care workers,"},{"time":412057,"text":"including beloved colleagues of mine,"},{"time":413975,"text":"five colleagues:\nMbalu Fonnie, Alex Moigboi,"},{"time":417746,"text":"Dr. Humarr Khan, Alice Kovoma\nand Mohamed Fullah."},{"time":421781,"text":"These are just five\nof many health-care workers"},{"time":424331,"text":"at Kenema and beyond"},{"time":426119,"text":"that died while the world waited\nand while we all worked,"},{"time":429179,"text":"quietly and separately."}]},{"cues":[{"time":431063,"text":"See, Ebola, like all threats to humanity,"},{"time":433120,"text":"it's fueled by mistrust\nand distraction and division."},{"time":437028,"text":"When we build barriers amongst ourselves\nand we fight amongst ourselves,"},{"time":440825,"text":"the virus thrives."},{"time":442669,"text":"But unlike all threats to humanity,"},{"time":444485,"text":"Ebola is one where\nwe're actually all the same."},{"time":447155,"text":"We're all in this fight together."},{"time":449059,"text":"Ebola on one person's doorstep\ncould soon be on ours."},{"time":452177,"text":"And so in this place\nwith the same vulnerabilities,"},{"time":455003,"text":"the same strengths,\nthe same fears, the same hopes,"},{"time":457440,"text":"I hope that we work together with joy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":462427,"text":"A graduate student of mine\nwas reading a book about Sierra Leone,"},{"time":465521,"text":"and she discovered that the word \"Kenema,\""},{"time":467879,"text":"the hospital that we work at and the city\nwhere we work in Sierra Leone,"},{"time":471346,"text":"is named after the Mende word\nfor \"clear like a river, translucent"},{"time":475551,"text":"and open to the public gaze.\""},{"time":477439,"text":"That was really profound for us,"},{"time":479008,"text":"because without knowing it,\nwe'd always felt"},{"time":481126,"text":"that in order to honor the individuals\nin Kenema where we worked,"},{"time":484334,"text":"we had to work openly, we had to share\nand we had to work together."},{"time":489074,"text":"And we have to do that."},{"time":490275,"text":"We all have to demand that\nof ourselves and others --"},{"time":494060,"text":"to be open to each other\nwhen an outbreak happens,"},{"time":496958,"text":"to fight in this fight together."},{"time":498632,"text":"Because this is not the first\noutbreak of Ebola,"},{"time":501565,"text":"it will not be the last,"},{"time":503037,"text":"and there are many other microbes\nout there that are lying in wait,"},{"time":506216,"text":"like Lassa virus and others."},{"time":507665,"text":"And the next time this happens,"},{"time":509198,"text":"it could happen in a city of millions,\nit could start there."},{"time":512418,"text":"It could be something\nthat's transmitted through the air."},{"time":515141,"text":"It could even be\ndisseminated intentionally."},{"time":517312,"text":"And I know that that is frightening,\nI understand that,"},{"time":520317,"text":"but I know also,\nand this experience shows us,"},{"time":522995,"text":"that we have the technology\nand we have the capacity"},{"time":526339,"text":"to win this thing,"},{"time":527958,"text":"to win this and have\nthe upper hand over viruses."},{"time":530828,"text":"But we can only do it if we do it together"},{"time":533124,"text":"and we do it with joy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":534871,"text":"So for Dr. Khan"},{"time":536416,"text":"and for all of those who sacrificed\ntheir lives on the front lines"},{"time":540606,"text":"in this fight with us always,"},{"time":543030,"text":"let us be in this fight with them always."},{"time":545861,"text":"And let us not let the world be defined"},{"time":547760,"text":"by the destruction wrought by one virus,"},{"time":549903,"text":"but illuminated by billions\nof hearts and minds"},{"time":552708,"text":"working in unity."}]},{"cues":[{"time":553940,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":555138,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}